benefits%20beyond%20logistics%20and%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20bringing%20young%20people%20from%20every%20nation%20together%2C%20%5Bthe%20Olympic%20Games%5D%20help%20foster%20this%20sense%20of%20cordiality%20that%20teaches%20men%20to%20become%20acquainted%20with%20each%20other%20better%20first%20and%20then%20to%20hold%20each%20other%20in%20higher%20esteem%2C%20a%20process%20that%20the%20Paris%20Games%20will%20have%20greatly%20aided%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Frantz%20Reichel%2C%20the%20secretary-general%20of%20the%20organizing%20committee%20of%20the%201924%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fioc%2Fnews%2Fthe-olympic-village-a-home-away-from-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Olympics.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20village%20was%20primitive%20by%20today's%20standards.%20The%20fenced-in%20area%20contained%20wooden%20huts%20separated%20by%20dirt%20paths.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20on%20a%20path%20between%20wooden%20huts%20in%20the%201924%20Paris%20Olympic%20Village.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ea698fb2b6bedb0594ceb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22994%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Olympic%20Village%20was%20comprised%20of%20modest%20wooden%20huts.%3Cp%3EARCHIVES%20CNOSF%2FArchives%20CNOSF%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20was%20built%20close%20to%20the%20Stade%20Olympique%20de%20Colombes%2C%20where%20many%20sporting%20events%20were%20held%20northwest%20of%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Olympics%20Studies%20Centre%2C%20its%20basic%20wooden%20huts%20were%20designed%20for%20three%20occupants%20each%2C%20with%20three%20beds%2C%20two%20basins%20for%20washing%2C%20and%20a%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20structures%20were%20separated%20by%20dirt%20paths%20that%20could%20be%20accessed%20by%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2Ffirst-olympic-village%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recognizes%20Paris%20as%20the%20home%20of%20the%20first%20Olympic%20Village%2C%20noted%20that%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Games%20in%201932%20that%20the%20Olympic%20Village%20featured%20%26quot%3Bkitchens%20and%20other%20modern%20amenities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDelegations%20paid%20for%20bed%20and%20board%2C%20which%20included%20food%2C%20laundry%2C%20and%20showers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Athletes%20sit%20in%20chairs%20outside%20a%20wooden%20hut%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Village%20in%20Paris%20in%201924.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ea54380d4d5da13d5f5f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAthletes%20relaxed%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Village%20in%20Paris%20in%201924.%3Cp%3ETopical%20Press%2FHulton%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETeams%20reserved%20beds%20by%20paying%20a%20deposit%2C%20and%20then%20they%20were%20charged%20daily%20rates%20for%20bed%20and%20board%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Olympic%20Studies%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAthletes%20were%20provided%20three%20meals%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20lunch%20and%20dinner%20included%20half%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221694%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Athletes%20sit%20at%20tables%20covered%20with%20white%20tablecloths%20at%20the%20catering%20hall%20of%20the%201924%20Olympic%20Village.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ea61e80d4d5da13d5f637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221402%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAthletes%20were%20offered%20three%20meals%20a%20day%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Village.%3Cp%3EARCHIVES%20CNOSF%2FArchives%20CNOSF%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3