tadium%2C%20the%20main%20events%20space%20for%20the%201924%20Olympics%20in%20Paris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ea80a80d4d5da13d5f6be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Colombes%20Olympic%20Stadium%20hosted%20events%20including%20athletics%2C%20football%2C%20horse%20riding%2C%20and%20fencing.%3Cp%3EARCHIVES%20CNOSF%2FArchives%20CNOSF%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%20a%20horse-racing%20track%20that%20opened%20in%201883%2C%20it%20became%20a%20stadium%20in%201907%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paris.fr%2Fen%2Fpages%2F1900-and-1924-paris-olympic-games-retrospective-27321%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis'%20tourism%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fparis-1924-the-olympic-games-come-of-age%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20fully%20renovated%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hold%2045%2C000%20spectators%20for%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stadium%20hosted%20the%20opening%20and%20closing%20ceremonies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sporting%20events%20such%20as%20equestrian%20events%2C%20football%2C%20rugby%2C%20track%20and%20field%2C%20and%20some%20pentathlons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Stade%20de%20Colombes%20was%20later%20renamed%20the%20Stade%20Yves-du-Manoir.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Ffr%2Fparis-2024%2Fsites%2Fstade-yves-du-manoir%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20host%20field%20hockey%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%202024%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENot%20every%20athlete%20competing%20in%20Paris%20stayed%20at%20the%20village.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cars%20outside%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20shooting%20range%20at%20Chalons-sur-Marnes%20at%20the%201924%20Paris%20Olympics.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F