rance%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKeeping%20coverage%20could%20provide%20peace%20of%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20that%20I%20outlined%20for%20keeping%20the%20pet%20insurance%20was%20two-fold%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EKnowing%20the%20coverage%20is%20there%20if%20needed%20can%20provide%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20dog%20would%20likely%20require%20more%20frequent%20and%20more%20varied%20medical%20care%20with%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20%26quot%3B-ologists%26quot%3B%20now%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20regular%20veterinarians.%20There%20are%20many%20more%20treatment%20options%20for%20various%20ailments%20that%20we%20didn't%20even%20have%20access%20to%20on%20behalf%20of%20our%20pets%2010%20or%2015%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20family%20felt%20they%20would%20want%20to%20take%20their%20dog%20to%20any%20available%20specialist%20needed%2C%20pet%20insurance%20would%20be%20a%20good%20thing%20to%20keep%20since%20they%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20Pet%20Insurance%20Quotes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Fbest-cheap-pet-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20pet%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20policies%20with%20Petted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20drop%20pet%20insurance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20client%20first%20got%20pet%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20their%20new%20puppy.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20insurance%20cost%20was%20fairly%20cheap%20at%20%2425%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Now%2C%20they%20had%20a%2010-year-old%20dog%20and%20an%20insurance%20policy%20that%20cost%20%24125%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20advised%20them%20that%20this%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsix%20one%20way%2C%20half-dozen%20the%20other%26quot%3B%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20dog%20was%20older%2C%20it%20was%20reasonable%20to%20assume%20more%20veterinary%20care%20was%20necessary.%20That's%20likely%20why%20their%20pet%20insurance%20premiums%20went%20up%3B%20a%2010-year-old%20dog%20is%20likely%20classified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20more%20expensive%20to%20insure%20regardless%20of%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20self-insure%20was%20one%20argument%20for%20dropping%20the%20coverage.%20Our%20client%20could%20cancel%20the%20contract%20and%20direct%20their%20%24125%20in%20premiums%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20earmarked%20for%20vet%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20had%20sufficient%20liquid%20assets%2C%20cash%20reserves%2C%20and%20strong%20income%20to%20handle%20a%20large%20medical%20cost%20should%20it%20occur%2C%20even%20without%20redirecting%20the%20old%20premium%20cost%20into%20their%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20reduce%20premiums%20on%20pet%20insurance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20client's%20question%20was%20not%20just%20whether%20they%20should%20keep%20insurance%20or%20not.%20They%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20what%20to%20do%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Faverage-cost-pet-insurance%5C%22%3Erising%20cost%20of%20pet%20insurance%20premiums%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20advised%20them%20that%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20insurance%2C%20the%20next%20step%20would%20be%20to%20get%20quotes%20from%20other%20carriers%20to%20compare%20the%20current%20policy%20to%20a%20new%20option%20from%20a%20different%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20any%20kind%20of%20insurance%20policy%2C%20pet%20or%20otherwise%2C%20I%20strongly%20recommend%20shopping%20around%20and%20getting%20at%20least%20three%20different%20quotes%20so%20you%20can%20compare%20coverages%20and%20rates