C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20stated%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20that%20the%20Atomic%20Minerals%20Directorate%20for%20Exploration%20and%20Research%20(AMD)%2C%20a%20constituent%20unit%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%2C%20has%20found%20the%20presence%20of%20Lithium%20resources%20in%20the%20Mandya%20and%20Yadgiri%20districts%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20informed%20the%20house%20that%20AMD%20has%20established%201%2C600%20tonnes%20(G3%20stage)%20of%20Lithium%20resources%20in%20the%20Marlagalla%20area%2C%20Mandya%20district%2C%20and%20preliminary%20surveys%20and%20limited%20subsurface%20exploration%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20Yadgiri%20district%20to%20know%20about%20the%20deposits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20AMD%20is%20carrying%20out%20exploration%20for%20Lithium%20in%20the%20potential%20geological%20domains%20in%20parts%20of%20Korba%20District%2C%20Chhattisgarh.%20However%2C%20the%20major%20mica%20belts%20located%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Pegmatite%20Belts%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20are%20the%20potential%20geological%20domains%20in%20the%20country%20for%20Lithium%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20shared%20that%20a%20preliminary%20survey%20carried%20out%20recently%20by%20AMD%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20led%20to%20the%20identification%20of%20surface%20uranium%20occurrence%20in%20Masanbal%2C%20Hamirpur%20district.%20He%20categorically%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%20has%20not%20conducted%20any%20study%20to%20establish%20an%20atomic%20energy%20plant%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20reply%20given%20by%20Singh%20in%20the%20upper%20house%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20is%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20developments%20and%20recent%20trends%20worldwide%20in%20the%20field%20of%20small%20modular%20reactors.%20While%20the%20different%20technologies%20and%20designs%20of%20small%20modular%20reactors%2C%20as%20published%20by%20different%20countries%20and%20foreign-based%20vendors%2C%20are%20being%20studied%20for%20gathering%20technical%20details%2C%20no%20proposal%20to%20collaborate%20with%20foreign%20vendors%2Fcountries%20is%20under%20consideration%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20that%2C%20at%20present%2C%20no%20private%20player%20has%20shown%20interest%20in%20producing%20a%20small%20modular%20reactor.%20However%2C%20a%20few%20private%20players%20have%20shown%20interest%20in%20deploying%20small%20reactors%20in%20their%20captive%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20added%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20have%20expressed%20interest%20in%20expanding%20cooperation%20in%20the%20field%20of%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20energy%20for%20peaceful%20purposes%2C%20including%20cooperation%20in%20the%20field%20of%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721994360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fp7tls288_rock-generic_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-600-tonnes-of-lithium-deposits-found-in-2-karnataka-districts-minister-6194321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lithium%20deposits%20have%20been%20found%20in%20the%20Mandya%20and%20Yadgiri%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20said%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20(Independent%20Charge)%20for%20Earth%20Sciences%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-600-tonnes-of-lithium-deposits-found-in-2-karnataka-districts-minister-6194321%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.