maraswamy%20alleged%20that%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20proposal%20was%20to%20exploit%20real%20estate%20opportunities%20in%20Ramanagara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20would%20reverse%20the%20plan%20when%20he%20becomes%20Chief%20Minister%20again.%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20JD(S)-BJP%20coalition%20when%20Ramanagara%20district%20was%20carved%20out%20in%20August%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Mr%20Kumarawamy's%20comments%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%20they%20won't%20come%20to%20power.%20So%20him%20(Kumaraswamy)%20reversing%20it%20is%20an%20illusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20earlier%20threatened%20to%20go%20on%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20if%20the%20government%20over%20the%20state%20government's%20plan%20to%20rename%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamanagara%20district%20is%20the%20political%20turf%20of%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20as%20he%20represented%20Ramanagara%20and%20Channapatna%20Assembly%20segments%2C%20and%20also%20had%20been%20an%20MP%20from%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20has%20gained%20significance%20ahead%20of%20Channapatna%20Assembly%20bypolls%20-%20the%20date%20for%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20-%20necessitated%20following%20Kumaraswamy's%20election%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Mandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721994300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F148jq9g8_ramanagara-karnataka_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-decides-to-rename-ramanagara-district-as-bengaluru-south-6194045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20rename%20Ramanagara%20district%20to%20Bengaluru%20South.%20The%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20Cabinet%20meeting%2C%20chaired%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%