0last%20year%20during%20the%20T20I%20series'%20against%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20Sharma%20announced%20his%20T20I%20retirement%20last%20month%2C%20Hardik%20didn't%20even%20get%20the%20vice-captaincy%2C%20with%20the%20selectors%20picking%20Shubman%20Gill%20for%20that%20role%20in%20both%20T20Is%20and%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20India%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20clarified%20that%20fitness%20and%20availability%20for%20all%20matches%20was%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20national%20selectors%20opted%20for%20Suryakumar%2C%20and%20not%20Hardik%2C%20who%20has%20had%20a%20history%20of%20injury%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20debate%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20captain%20Rashid%20Latif%20has%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Indian%20selectors%2C%20saying%20that%20fitness%20is%20just%20an%20excuse%20for%20not%20making%20Hardik%20the%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20here%20they%20(the%20claims)%20should%20just%20hand%20him%20a%20certificate%20saying%20he%20isn't%20fit%20and%20there%20are%20concerns%20about%20his%20fitness.%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20players%20who%20weren't%20super%20fit%20but%20still%20became%20great%20captains.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20just%20an%20excuse.%20Because%20if%20Surya%20wasn't%20around%2C%20then%20Rishabh%20(Pant)%20would%20have%20been%20the%20captain%20since%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Latif%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20three-match%20series%20will%20begin%20on%20July%2027%20in%20Pallekele%2C%20followed%20by%20matches%20on%20July%2028%20and%2030%20at%20the%20same%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20T20I%20Squad%3A%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(C)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20(VC)%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20Riyan%20Parag%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(WK)%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%20(WK)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Shivam%20Dube%2