%20over%20a%20croque%20madame%20(a%20French%20sandwich)%20is%20the%20quintessential%20Parisian%20experience.%20But%20as%20a%20wine%20and%20spirits%20writer%2C%20I%20appreciate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-cocktails-to-order-at-bar-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20good%20cocktail%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20charming%20Le%20Marais%20neighborhood%20is%20full%20of%20renowned%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20singular%20ingredient-focused%20drinks%20at%20Little%20Red%20Door%2C%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theworlds50best.com%2Fbars%2Fthe-list%2Flittle-red-door.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20world's%2050%20best%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20fabulous%20gin%2C%20aquavit%2C%20and%20fino%20sherry%20drink%20at%20The%20Cambridge%20Public%20House%2C%20a%20cross%20between%20a%20pub%20and%20cocktail%20lounge.%20I%20ended%20the%20night%20with%20a%20savory%20olive%20oil%20and%20balsamic%20martini%20riff%20at%20Le%20Mary%20Celeste%2C%20a%20cozy%20bar%20with%20an%20extensive%20wine%20list%2C%20and%20a%20spicy%20marg%20at%20La%20Mezcaleria%2C%20a%20cocktail%20bar%20inside%20the%201K%20Hotel%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22291aea10-527c-41b2-91bc-1e851594eb1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20you're%20waiting%20for%20the%20Notre-Dame%20Cathedral%20to%20reopen%2C%20head%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBasilica%20de%20Sacr%C3%A9%20Coeur%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20palatial%20building%20with%20three%20peaks%2C%20two%20stairways%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%20and%20statues%20at%20the%20front.%20The%20building%20sits%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill%20and%20is%20surrounded%20by%20trees%20and%20a%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66968e109caa6ed01e0200c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Basilica%20de%20Sacr%C3%A9%20Coeur%20is%20a%20beautiful%2C%20impressive%20church.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20visit%20the%20Notre-Dame%20Cathedral%20several%20times%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnotre-dame-cathedral-paris-fire-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emassive%20fire%20in%202019%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Fen%2Ffrance%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2Ffive-years-after-fire-notre-dame-cathedral-s-restoration-is-nearly-complete_6668514_7.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escheduled%20to%20open%20later%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20must-see%20if%20you're%20visiting%20Paris%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20suggest%20visiting%20the%20Basilique%20du%20Sacr%C3%A9-C%C5%93ur%20de%20Montmartre%2C%20which%20is%20perched%20high%20atop%20the%20Montmartre%20hill%20and%20features%20great%20views%20of%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaying-at-hotel-that-used-to-be-church-amsterdam-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20church%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20walked%20through%20the%20restaurants%20and%20shops%20in%20the%20bustling%20Montmartre%20district%C2%A0and%20then%20took%20in%20the%20view%20atop%20the%20steps%20leading%20to%20the%20basilica.%20On%20some%20of%20my%20visits%2C%20I've%20even%20heard%20live%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20walked%20down%20the%20steps%20and%20grabbed%20a%20table%20at%20Le%20Studio%20Caf%C3%A9.%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20the%20food%20is%20especially%20note-worthy%2C%20but%20the%20restaurant%20boasts%20an%20enviable%20view%20of%20the%20Basilique%20du%20Sacr%C3%A9-C%C5%93u.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d73d90f-b528-45c3-9c62-7c7f5ef1f8eb%5C%22%3EOnce%20you've%20had%20your%20fill%20of%20cr%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%C3%AA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong