%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20genuine%20art%20piece%20to%20take%20home%2C%20a%20friend%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20matching%20tattoos%20at%20Freaks%20and%20Geeks%20Tattoo%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20another%20customer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoo-tips-disney-designs-from-artist-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20inked%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20adorable%20cheeseboard%20design%20while%20we%20waited%20to%20get%20our%20Champagne-flute%20tattoos.%20This%20past%20summer%2C%20I%20returned%20for%20a%20lavender-sprig%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shop%20has%20talented%20artists%2C%20and%20the%20tattoos%20are%20my%20all-time%20favorite%20souvenirs%20from%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-things-to-do-not-touristy-from-frequent-traveler-2024%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721991842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669693979caa6ed01e020404%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-things-to-do-not-touristy-from-frequent-traveler-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Montparnasse%20Tower%20and%20Les%20Catacombes%20are%20some%20of%20the%20best%20places%20to%20go%20in%20Paris%20after%20hitting%20the%20touristy%20spots%2C%20a%20frequent%20traveler%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Magyarics)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-things-to-do-not-touristy-from-frequent-traveler-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunita%20Williams%20Stuck%20In%20Space%2C%20Still%20No%20Clue%20How%20She'll%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFifty%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20remains%20in%20limbo%2C%20uncertain%20of%20when%20and%20how%20she%20may%20return%20to%20Earth.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20maintains%20that%20she%20and%20the%20eight%20other%20astronauts%20on%20board%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20are%20safe%20and%20in%20'good%20spirits'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20space%20expert%2C%20speaking%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20humour%2C%20likened%20her%20situation%20to%20being%20in%20a%20state%20of%20'Trishanku'-a%20state%20where%20one%20is%20indeterminably%20but%20willingly%20stuck%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20NASA%20provided%20further%20updates%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20are%20closer%20to%20identifying%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner's%20malfunctioning%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20the%20failed%20thrusters%20and%20a%20series%20of%20helium%20leaks%20during%20its%20maiden%20test%20flight.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20clarity%20on%20when%2C%20or%20if%2C%20Astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20her%20crewmate%20Butch%20Wilmore%20will%20return%2C%20or%20if%20they%20will%20do%20so%20aboard%20the%20same%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Boeing%2C%20the%20Starliner%20can%20remain%20docked%20with%20the%20space%20station%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20ninety%20days%2C%20after%20which%20the%20batteries%20on%20board%20the%20spacecraft%20may%20deplete.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20US%20space%20technologists%20have%20approximately%20forty%20days%20left%20to%20determine%20whether%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20will%20return%20to%20Earth%20on%20the%20impaired%20Boeing%20Starliner%2C%20or%20if%20they%20will%20use%20SpaceX's%20Crew%20Dragon%20or%20the%20Russian%20Soyuz%20spacecraft.%20Both%20these%20standby%20vehicles%20are%20already%20docked%20at%20the%20space%20station%2C%20so%20neither%20Sunita%20Williams%20nor%20the%20other%20eight%20astronauts%20are%20truly%20stranded%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20Commercial%20Crew%20Program%20Manager%20Steve%20Stich%20noted%20that%20the%20crew%20is%20in%20good%20spirits%20and%20making%20the%20most%20of%20their%20time%20on%20the%20station%20as%20part%20of%20Expedition%2071%2C%20given%20that%20both%20Sunita%20and%20Butch%20have%20previously%20undertaken%20long-duration%20missions.%20He%20added%20that%20%60contingency%20plans'%20are%20in%20place%2C%20but%20the%20current%20effort%20is%20focused%20on%20bringing%20both%20Sunita%20and%20Butch%20back%20to%20Earth%20on%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20a%20brave%20face%20on%20the%20situation%2C%20Mark%20Nappi%2C%20Starliner%20program%20manager%20and%20vice%20president%20of%20Boeing%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20confident%20we%20have%20a%20good%20vehicle%20%5Bin%20Boeing%20Starliner%5D%20to%20bring%20the%20crew%20back%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20encountered%20several%20setbacks%20during%20the%20Starliner's%20development.%20Originally%20contracted%20for%20%244.2%20billion%2C%20the%20company%20has%20now%20spent%20approximately%20%245.7%20billion%2C%20with%20the%20mission%20still%20incomplete.%20NASA%20sought%20a%20second%20alternative%20to%20SpaceX's%20Crew%20Dragon%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Boeing%20Starliner%20was%20being%20developed.%20Boeing%20is%20also%20facing%20broader%20difficulties%2C%20with%20its%20aviation%20and%20aircraft%20business%20stumbling%2C%20and%20recently%2C%20Boeing%20CEO%20David%20Calhoun%20was%20questioned%20by%20US%20Senators%20regarding%20the%20company's%20safety%20culture%20and%20transparency%20during%20a%20US%20Congress%20appearance.%20If%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20fails%20to%20return%20the%20two%20astronauts%20to%20Earth%2C%20it%20would%20represent%20a%20significant%20setback%20for%20this%20aerospace%20and%20space%20technology%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20today%2C%20NASA%20said%2C%20'With%20ground%20testing%20of%20a%20Reaction%20Control%20System%20(RCS)%20thruster%20complete%20and%20disassembly%20and%20inspections%20concluding%2C%20the%20Starliner%20team%20is%20reviewing%20data%20that%20will%20aid%20in%20future%20missions%20and%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20NASA%20astronauts%20Butch%20Wilmore%20and%20Sunita%20Williams%20to%20return%20to%20Earth.%20A%20landing%20date%20for%20the%20Starliner%20Crew%20Flight%20Test%20(CFT)%20will%20be%20scheduled%20following%20the%20Flight%20Test%20Readiness%20Review%20planned%20for%20later%20next%20week%2C%20with%20landing%20opportunities%20available%20throughout%20August.%20Testing%20of%20the%20RCS%20thruster%20at%20NASA's%20White%20Sands%20Test%20Facility%20in%20New%20Mexico%20yielded%20meaningful%20findings%20for%20root%20cause%20assessments%20and%20to%20finalise%20flight%20rationale%20in%20support%20of%20a%20nominal%20undock%20and%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Starliner%20team%20plans%20to%20hot-fire%2027%20of%2028%20RCS%20thrusters%20this%20weekend%20while%20safely%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station.%20This%20test%20aims%20to%20verify%20thruster%20performance%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20would%20be%20done%20during%20future%20missions.%20The%20team%20also%20seeks%20another%20data%20point%20on%20helium%20leaks%2C%20which%20have%20remained%20stable%20since%20the%20spacecraft's%20arrival%20at%20the%20station%20on%20June%206.%20The%20helium%20system%20has%20been%20closed%20for%20most%20of%20the%20time%20while%20docked%2C%20so%20no%20helium%20is%20leaking%20in%20that%20configuration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%2C%20'Additionally%2C%20NASA%20and%20Boeing%20will%20conduct%20a%20second%20docked%20hot-fire%20test%20over%20the%20weekend%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20spacecraft's%20thruster%20performance.%20The%20first%20docked%20hot-fire%20test%20occurred%20on%20June%2015.%20The%20upcoming%20test%20will%20allow%20checks%20of%20the%20helium%20leaks%20while%20also%20verifying%20that%20the%20thrusters%20are%20operating%20as%20expected.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20glitches%20were%20anticipated%20during%20this%20maiden%20test%20flight%2C%20the%20extension%20of%20a%20ten-day%20mission%20to%20over%20five%20times%20its%20expected%20duration%2C%20with%20no%20end%20date%20in%20sight%2C%20is%20deeply%20concerning%20for%20the%20global%20space%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721991780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F720ksnho_sunita-williams_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-stuck-in-space-still-no-clue-on-how-shell-return-6193495%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fifty%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20remains%20in%20limbo%2C%20uncertain%20of%20when%20and%20how%20she%20may%20return%20to%20Earth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-stuck-in-space-still-no-clue-on-how-shell-return-6193495%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-stuck-in-space-still-no-clue-on-how-shell-return-6193495%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-stuck-in-space-still-no-clue-on-how-shell-return-6193495%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Elon%20Musk%20could%20benefit%20from%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666aae59764df16112595584%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump%3Cp%3ELisa%20O'Connor%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%20and%20AP%20Photo%2FChris%20Carlson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20championed%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidential%20campaign.%3C%2Fli%3