0some%20point%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202024%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-cpi-june-prices-food-energy-fed-interest-rate-cuts-2024-7%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Price%20Index%20rose%203.0%25%20year-over-year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Inflation%20has%20slowed%20significantly%20since%20it%20peaked%20last%20year%2C%20which%20means%20mortgage%20rates%20should%20soon%20start%20trending%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20homeowners%20looking%20to%C2%A0leverage%20their%20home's%20value%C2%A0to%20cover%20a%20big%20purchase%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20home%20renovation%20%E2%80%94%20a%C2%A0home%20equity%20line%20of%20credit%20(HELOC)%20may%20be%20a%20good%20option%20while%20we%20wait%20for%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20ease.%20Check%20out%20some%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-heloc-lenders%5C%22%3Ebest%20HELOC%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20start%20your%20search%20for%20the%20right%20loan%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20HELOC%20is%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20that%20lets%20you%20borrow%20against%20the%20equity%20in%20your%20home.%20It%20works%20similarly%20to%20a%20credit%20card%20in%20that%20you%20borrow%20what%20you%20need%20rather%20than%20getting%20the%20full%20amount%20you're%20borrowing%20in%20a%20lump%20sum.%20It%20also%20lets%20you%20tap%20into%20the%20money%20you%20have%20in%20your%20home%20without%20replacing%20your%20entire%20mortgage%2C%20like%20you'd%20do%20with%20a%20cash-out%20refinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider