%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-ministers-in-china-plead-for-debt-relief%2Farticleshow%2F112039087.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-ministers-in-china-plead-for-debt-relief%2Famp_articleshow%2F112039087.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-ministers-in-china-plead-for-debt-relief%2Famp_articleshow%2F112039087.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kids%20to%20Senior%20Citizens%2C%20Anyone%20Can%20Use%20This%20Techie%E2%80%99s%20DIY%20Handloom%20Kit%20To%20Weave%20Fabric%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKalaiyarasi%20Ramachandran%20spent%20her%20childhood%20admiring%20the%20large%20handlooms%20in%20the%20quaint%20weavers%E2%80%99%20lanes%20of%20Salangapalayam%20village%20in%20Erode%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20rhythmic%20sound%20of%20looms%20and%20transformation%20of%20yarn%20into%20nine%20yards%20of%20sarees%20diligently%20woven%20by%20the%20weavers%20was%20magical%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20carefully%20watch%20the%20fine%20threads%20being%20woven%20in%20the%20loom.%20We%20would%20fear%20sitting%20near%20the%20weavers%20as%20the%20work%20required%20focus%20and%20no%20distraction.%20I%20would%20be%20tasked%20with%20small%20works%20like%20rotating%20the%20spinning%20wheel.%20We%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraatai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spinning%20wheel)%20in%20our%20house%2C%20so%20I%20would%20sneak%20to%20the%20weavers%E2%80%99%20homes%20and%20admire%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20grew%20up%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20went%20on%20to%20study%20computer%20science%20and%20secured%20a%20well-paying%20job%20at%20an%20IT%20company%20in%20Chennai%20as%20a%20developer.%20A%20turning%20point%20cam