e%20into%20a%20declining%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308649%2Fanshul-malhotra-krishna-wools-preserves-himachal-handloom-designs-helps-weavers-earn%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandloom%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20same%20area%20as%20those%20weavers.%20I%20felt%20like%20doing%20something%20for%20the%20society%20and%20reviving%20this%20art%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalaiyarasi%20spoke%20to%20weavers%20to%20understand%20the%20gaps%20behind%20this%20waning%20art.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20to%20know%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20do%20not%20want%20to%20engage%20in%20weaving.%20The%20loom%20also%20occupies%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20typically%20taking%206%C3%976%20feet%20area%20in%20the%20room%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2036-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20work%20interesting%20and%20engaging%2C%20she%20manufactured%20DIY%20handloom%20kits%20with%20the%20help%20of%20weavers.%20They%20help%20her%20with%20the%20designs%20and%20assembling%20of%20the%20looms%20with%20the%20process%20taking%20anywhere%20between%202-5%20days.%20Occupying%20less%20space%2C%20it%20can%20be%20used%20by%20anyone%2C%20from%20children%20to%20senior%20citizens%20to%20weave%20fabrics%20from%20yarns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Raatai%20Handloom%E2%80%99%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20introduced%20three%20kinds%20of%20looms.%20At%20the%20first%20level%20is%20%E2%80%98WeaveMate%E2%80%99%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20loom%20frame%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20purses%2C%20wall%20hangings%2C%20mats%2C%20coasters%2C%20and%20pouches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20second%20level%20is%20%E2%80%98WeaveAlly%E2%80%99%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20slightly%20bigger%20products%20like%20handbags%2C%20stoles%2C%20scarves%2C%20headbands%2C%20and%20table%20runners.%20At%20the%20third%20level%2C%20she%20has%20%E2%8