the%20other%20way%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2020-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20the%20screenshot%20of%20an%20online%20post%20by%20Musk%20that%20claimed%20Wilson%20was%20born%20%26quot%3Bgay%20and%20slightly%20autistic%26quot%3B%20-%20which%20the%20Tesla%20boss%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Battributes%20that%20contribute%20to%20gender%20dysphoria%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20from%20when%20he%20was%20about%204%20years%20old%20and%20he%20would%20pick%20out%20clothes%20for%20me%20to%20wear%20like%20a%20jacket%20and%20tell%20me%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bfabulous!%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20love%20of%20musicals%20%26amp%3B%20theatre.%20But%20he%20was%20not%20a%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20Musk's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPost%20by%20%40vivllainous%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40vivllainous%2Fpost%2FC91xDGJSUX_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20entirely%20fake%2C%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20Wilson.%20%26quot%3BLike%2C%20literally%20none%20of%20this%20ever%20happened.%20Ever.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20where%20he%20got%20this%20from.%20My%20best%20guess%20is%20that%20he%20went%20to%20the%20Milo%20Yiannopoulis%20school%20of%20gay%20stereotypes%2C%20just%20picked%20some%20at%20random%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Beh-%20good%20enough%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20garner%20sympathy%20points%20when%20he%20is%20so%20obviously%20in%20the%20wrong%20even%20in%20his%20own%20fu**ing%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Wilson%20denied%20that%20she%20ever%20picked%20jackets%20for%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20most%20certainly%20not%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bfabulous%26quot%3B%20because%20literally%20what%20the%20f**k.%20I%20did%20not%20use%20the%20word%20fabulous%20when%20I%20was%20four%20because%20once%20again%20I%20would%20like%20to%20reiterate...%20I%20was%20four%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20she%20did%20not%20have%20her%20father%20by%20her%20side%20when%20she%20was%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20entire%20thing%20is%20completely%20made%20up%20and%20there's%20a%20reason%20for%20this.%20He%20doesn't%20know%20what%20I%20was%20like%20as%20a%20child%20because%20he%20quite%20simply%20wasn't%20there%2C%20and%20in%20the%20little%20time%20that%20he%20was%20I%20was%20relentlessly%20harassed%20for%20my%20femininity%20and%20queerness.%20Obviously%20he%20can't%20say%20that%2C%20so%20I've%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20happy%20little%20stereotype%20f*g-ing%20along%20to%20use%20at%20his%20discretion.%20I%20think%20that%20says%20alot%20about%20how%20he%20views%20queer%20people%20and%20children%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20sought%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20over%20her%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20legally%20recognized%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20state%20of%20California%20and%20I%20don't%20concern%20myself%20with%20the%20opinions%20of%20those%20who%20are%20below%20me.%20Obviously%20Elon%20can't%20say%20the%20same%20because%20in%20a%20ketamine-fueled%20haze%2C%20he's%20desperate%20for%20attention%20and%20validation%20from%20an%20army%20of%20degenerate%20red-pilled%20incels%20and%20pick-mes%20who%20are%20quick%20to%20give%20it%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20had%20hit%20the%20headlines%20earlier%20this%20month%20with%20his%20claim%20about%20Wilson%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20conservative%20commentator%20Jordan%20Peterson.%20He%20had%20also%20accused%20those%20involved%20in%20promoting%20gender-affirming%20care%20of%20targeting%20children%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20far%20below%20the%20age%20of%20consent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20tricked%20into%20doing%20this.%20I%20lost%20my%20son%2C%20essentially.%20They%20call%20it%20'deadnaming'%20for%20a%20reason.%20The%20reason%20they%20call%20it%20'deadnaming'%20is%20because%20your%20son%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20experience%20set%20him%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20combat%20what%20he%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bwoke%20mind%20virus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20the%20woke%20mind%20virus%20after%20that.%20And%20we're%20making%20some%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivian%20Jenna%20Wilson%20had%20legally%20changed%20her%20name%20and%20gender%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20She%20had%20then%20asserted%20she%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20related%20to%20Musk%2C%20her%20biological%20father.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Justine%20Wilson%2C%20had%20divorced%20Musk%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721984520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8trrs42_elon-musk_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disowned-by-transgender-daughter-hes-desperate-for-attention-6193039%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20estranged%20transgender%20daughter%2C%20who%20he%20had%20alleged%20was%20%26quot%3Bkilled%26quot%3B%20by%20%26quot%3Bwoke%20mind%20virus%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20%26quot%3Bdisowned%26quot%3B%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-disowned-by-transgender-daughter-hes-desperate-for-at