it%2C%20and%20saw%20almost%20500%20people%20get%20interviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20change%20diversity%20ratios%20in%20organisations%20by%20initiating%20conversations%20and%20influencing%20decisions%20by%20showcasing%20that%20hiring%20based%20on%20DEI%20(Diversity%2C%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion)%20is%20the%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha%20Sable%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Vividhataa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open-to-all%20DEI%20seminar%2Fconference%20was%20attended%20by%20corporate%20delegates%20along%20with%20students%2C%20researchers%2C%20experts%2C%20DE%26amp%3BI%20advocates%2C%20and%20similar%20activists%20from%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20panel%20discussions%2C%20fireside%20chats%2C%20and%20interactive%20workshops%20such%20as%20one-on-one%20sign%20language%20were%20held%20at%20the%20event.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20promoting%20empathy%20and%20understanding%2C%20Vividhataa%20plans%20to%20make%20DEI%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20and%20global%20MNCs%20across%20India%20through%20its%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20in%202020%20and%20traditional%20job%20fairs%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20place%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Vividhataa%20filled%20the%20gap%20by%20launching%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%201st%20Virtual%20Diversity%20Job%20Fair%202020%E2%80%9D%20to%20support%20minority%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20fair%20saw%20lots%20of%20diverse%20candidates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%2