%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-1046x1536.jpeg%201046w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-150x220.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357938%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20introduced%20comprehensive%20changes%20to%20the%20farm%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352547%2Ffarmers-income-aneesh-jain-gram-unnati-value-chain-rajasthan-agri-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstallation%20of%20a%20biodigester%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20improvements%20to%20cow%20management%2C%20culminating%20in%20value%20addition.%20He%20also%20implemented%20a%20solar%20dryer%20for%20post-harvest%20management.%20Students%20and%20farmers%20from%20across%20South%20India%20visit%20his%20farm%20to%20attend%20his%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sreedhu%2C%20adding%20that%20more%20youngsters%20must%20consider%20this%20path%20instead%20of%20running%20to%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20facing%20a%20nutritional%20crisis%20today%20due%20to%20the%20food%20that%20is%20grown%20and%20consumed.%20The%20younger%20generation%20must%20get%20into%20farming%20and%20go%20back%20to%20the%20way%20things%20were%20done%20before%20%E2%80%94%20organic%20and%20adding%20technology%20where%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20consider%20that%20while%20we%20focus%20on%20increasing%20our%20bank%20balances%20and%20securing%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20financial%20future%2C%20we%20are%20only%20providing%20them%20with%20financial%20security.%20What%20about%20ensuring%20their%20food%20security%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courte